    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like something that's just gonna fade. everything feels empty. like there's no point in even trying to fix it or talk to anyone because the person i actually want to talk to isn't here. it's just a massive, hollow weight in my chest. i feel like i'm just existing, but i'm not actually living anymore.",
